casebody.data:
Burl Anderson HOWELL
v.
NORTH CAROLINA WAYNE COUNTY DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES hereinafter NCWCDHHS, by and through, Resee PHELPS; Lou Jones. No. 326P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 5, 2015.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Petitioner on the 22nd of September 2015 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Office of Administrative Hearings, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of November 2015."
